Overview

Visits:

1

Do not miss out on this tastefully, updated home sitting on a corner lot! The open inviting floor plan and large backyard makes it perfect to host family and friends. The gourmet kitchen offers customs cabinets, quartz counter tops and large kitchen island with brand new appliances. This home features 3 spacious bedrooms equipped with ceiling fans and walk-in closets. The master bath has been renovated to make full use of every space, with a oversized, gorgeous shower and a rain fall shower head. Additional updates include LED recessed lights, luxury vinyl planks, fresh paint and windows. Saginaw West Estates is a sought after community located less than a mile to restaurants & shopping areas. Approximately 25 minutes to DFW airport, 15 minutes to down town Fort Worth, and 10 minutes to the famous Texas Stock Yards!
